import { createApp } from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import './assets/tailwind.css'

import { library } from '@fortawesome/fontawesome-svg-core'
import { FontAwesomeIcon } from '@fortawesome/vue-fontawesome'
import {
  faTshirt, faSocks, faUserTie, faShoePrints, faGift, faPlusCircle, faMagic, faChevronLeft, faChevronRight,
  faHeart, faHeart as faHeartSolid, faArrowRight, faCloud, faChartBar, faCloudUploadAlt, faTimes, faSun, faLayerGroup,
  faArrowUp, faChartPie, faTint, faVest, faFemale, faStar, faPersonDress, faGlasses
} from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons'
import { faBell as faBellO, faUser as faUserO, faSun as faSunO, faHeart as faHeartO } from '@fortawesome/free-regular-svg-icons'

library.add(
  faTshirt, faSocks, faUserTie, faShoePrints, faGift, faPlusCircle, faMagic, faChevronLeft, faChevronRight,
  faHeart, faHeartSolid, faArrowRight, faCloud, faChartBar, faCloudUploadAlt, faTimes, faSun, faLayerGroup,
  faArrowUp, faChartPie, faTint, faVest, faFemale, faStar, faPersonDress, faGlasses,
  faBellO, faUserO, faSunO, faHeartO
)

const app = createApp(App)
app.component('font-awesome-icon', FontAwesomeIcon)
app.mount('#app')
